# FRI Portal Module Development Guidelines

## Survey System Module

### Dynamic Survey Engine Requirements

- Support adaptive questioning based on previous answers
- Implement sector-specific logic for targeted questions
- Calculate progress accurately based on completed questions
- Validate answers according to question requirements
- Handle skip conditions and branching logic
- Support multiple question types (multiple choice, text, rating, etc.)

### Auto-Save & Resume Functionality

- Implement debounced auto-save to prevent excessive API calls
- Save progress at regular intervals (every 2-3 seconds)
- Handle network failures gracefully with retry logic
- Allow users to resume from where they left off
- Clear saved data after successful submission
- Provide visual feedback for save status

### ACRA Integration

- Auto-fill company data from ACRA API
- Allow manual override of auto-filled data
- Cache ACRA data to reduce API calls
- Handle API failures gracefully
- Validate ACRA numbers before submission
- Support batch company data import

